messages.about.title: Welcome to the CollectionSpace Materials Authority Demo
messages.about.contentHTML:
CollectionSpace is a free, open-source collections management application for museums, historical societies, natural science collections, and more.

This demo site is running the current version of the materials authority profile of CollectionSpace. If youâ€™re interested in a version of CollectionSpace configured to meet the needs of a specific domain, please visit our demo landing page to view all available options. Examples include Anthropology, Botanical Garden, Fine Art, Herbarium, and Local History & Material Culture.

To log in, use the email admin@materials.collectionspace.org, with the case-sensitive password Administrator. To view in read-only mode, use the email reader@materials.collectionspace.org with the password reader.

Not sure where to get started? Follow along with one of our quick-start guides:

  • Create a new object: PDF Screencast
  • Link to an image: PDF Screencast
  • Add a storage location: PDF Screencast

We rebuild this demo site weekly so don't worry, you won't break it!
